# Build artifacts and provider binaries
**/.terraform/
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Terraform local artifacts — never commit state, plans, or real variable files
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/tfplan
**/*.tfplan
**/*.tfvars
!**/*.tfvars.example

# Local dev artifacts
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
*.zip
*.eml
.playwright-last-results.json

# Personal / local config
**/appsettings.Personal.json
.github/agents/
.github/copilot-instructions.md
MANIFEST.md
